    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "The \"balanced perspective\" is exactly what the CAA is implementing by bringing in a more diverse group of controllers from different global regions to avoid the rigidness of an AI. We believe a wide range of human perspectives makes the system more resilient. Are you suggesting that these human controllers, even with their diverse backgrounds and training, are somehow a risk to the efficiency of the corridor?",
